Package cmpt355.project.language

Class ArrayType

java.lang.Object
cmpt355.project.language.DataType
cmpt355.project.language.ArrayType
public final class ArrayType
extends DataType
A class representing an array type, e.g. an int[] or String[][]. An ArrayType has a base type (e.g int or String) and a (positive) dimension (the number of []s). Normally ArrayType objects are created by DataType.arrayOf(DataType) or DataType.arrayOf(DataType, int).
